Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.11,0:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Am I the first one here today?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, morning, Ayane{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.72,0:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To everyone at the Abydos Task Force:
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, sorry for saying goodbye via letter.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.23,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For starters, sorry for saying goodbye via letter.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.23,0:02:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you're my age,\nyou prefer the more old-fashioned ways.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.74,0:02:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've actually been receiving offers for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.66,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They want me to work as a mercenary for Kaiser PMC.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.00,0:02:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In exchange, they'll pay over half\nof the debt Abydos owes them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.59,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may not look like it,\nbut I've actually got a bit of a reputation.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I got all preachy back at the Black Market,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.01,0:02:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'm sorry for going back on my own words.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.29,0:02:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this should at least give\nthe Task Force some breathing room.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the final member of the student council,\nthis is my responsibility to bear.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To {*}our teacher{*Sensei}:
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not exactly a secret, \Nbut I used to hate adults.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day Shiroko{**-chan} brought you to our clubroom,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.93,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I immediately assumed you were\njust another no-good adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.25,0:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you broke down those walls immediately.\nYou're part of the team now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm leaving them in your care, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're their teacher. They trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.83,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad I got to meet an adult like you before I...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, that's more than enough sappy stuff for one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nonomi{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serika{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do this for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Protect our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.35,0:03:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure, it may be covered in sand and dust,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it's all I have left.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And one last thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.94,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may end up having to fight\neach other as enemies one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day that happens,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.12,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to destroy my halo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She literally {\i1}just{\i0} told us people\ndo crazy things when desperate!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she think we'll accept this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.01,0:04:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go find her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to help her!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! We need to assess the situation first.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hoshino{**-senpai}'s—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep firing until the area's secure!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.55,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Abydos student council's\nlast remaining member has quit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.19,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Kaiser Corporation,\nwill seize control of Abydos High School!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Several hundred Kaiser PMC troops on approach!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,ED,They're firing indiscriminately in the city! {"firing on" would work better than "firing in" here I think --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all times, why now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to engage.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stay calm.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuating civilians takes top priority.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm hanging in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.81,0:05:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not sure, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreclosure Task Force spotted! Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to someplace safe for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get a grip!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You get that side!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.12,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! These guys are tough!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They just keep coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hold the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I had intended to face you at the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I appreciate you meeting me halfway,\nstudents of Abydos High School.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just attacking the city at this point!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.89,0:06:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you own the land here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing gives you the right to do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.63,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the school still belongs to Abydos!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of invasion is a clear violation of the law!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll report you to the GSC!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You scumbags!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Hoshino{**-senpai} back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.46,0:07:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all going on about?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You think reporting me will do anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.38,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting little theory.\nWhy don't you test it out right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.95,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already begged them for help\ncountless times before, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.81,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it ever amount to anything?\nDid they ever lift up a finger to help you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you finally understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.79,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle all you want. Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.69,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And now Takanashi Hoshino, the last vestige\nof the student council, has dropped out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.21,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos no longer has a student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.55,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are no longer anybody at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.19,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Student council or no,\nAbydos still has the Task Force!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away with that while we're still—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.97,0:08:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Task Force isn't an\nofficially sanctioned organisation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.99,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.91,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.86,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time we formed the Task Force,\nthe student council was already defunct{/gone}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.42,0:08:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.60,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're merely an unofficial club.\n No documentation, no official approval.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.74,0:08:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you have nothing to prove that you exist!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's the good news.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Abydos High is no more,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.87,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll finally be free of that debt for good!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that happens, what about\nall the hard work we've put in so far?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.13,0:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you actually planning on paying back your debt\nover the next couple hundred years?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.33,0:08:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you were simply waiting for\na convenient excuse to end this charade.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}did{\i0} you all work so hard, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it all for?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you... If you say one more word...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will fighting here even change anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.97,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we stop them here,\nwhat happens afterwards?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.51,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we somehow took back our school,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.25,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we still have a huge debt to pay off.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.10,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The land we lost won't magically come back, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, Hoshino{**-senpai}'s gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The student council is gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.31,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nothing but an unofficial club.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What more could we even do?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.01,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why us and nobody else?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A large explosion reported north of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.81,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo Platoon got caught in the blast!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? {NANI}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosions to the east, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.12,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mike Platoon got hit by a massive C4 explosion—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.61,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than listen to\nyour pathetic wailing for a moment longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"An eye for an eye."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"A tooth for a tooth."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.52,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"We tread a path none may follow,\nand do so without mercy."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.37,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that your motto, Masked Swimsuit Gang?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't fall for a bunch of pushovers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chillax, Aru{**-chan}. {### I WILL DIE ON THIS HILL}{Then perish. --ik}{based -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They get the message.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls with glasses are quite delicate.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't help but crack under pressure.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know what?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.84,0:10:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a girl with glasses cry,\nand there'll be hell to pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you asked for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna paint the town red with your guts!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.69,0:11:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to tell right from left, wrong from right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.61,0:11:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Every path you take leads to failure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.45,0:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And even once you stumble down the right one,\nall that awaits you is another dark tunnel.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Backup is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.93,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend's in danger, isn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.65,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just gonna sit there feeling sorry\nwhile they take everything from you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take this lying down?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me you're such pathetic cowards?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Problem Solver!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.36,0:11:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but lowly dogs!\nHow dare you turn on me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, put a lid on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.60,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I much prefer working with these girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.25,0:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural for a villain to stab\ntheir employer in the back, no?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoken like a true villain.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.33,0:12:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the pep talk we needed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to doubt ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Who cares if we're unofficial?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.01,0:12:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got bigger things to worry about!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}will{\i0} save Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else is secondary.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You still want to waste your time\nwith this pointless resistance?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.99,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No! How dare {\i1}you{\i0} torment my precious student?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking Hoshino back!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.57,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can just come out of nowhere\nand start making demands?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then, I have just the thing for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But sir, it's still a prototype!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to deploy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.79,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach them what it means to defy me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This exosuit is the pinnacle of\nour company's technology!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.73,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Its armaments and armour are crafted\nfrom the finest materials.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the cutting edge of weaponry!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! It's so big!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This could get messy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,True, this won't be easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only if it's us four.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Back us up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alley-oop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a dent.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just cheating!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to be caught\non the business end of those.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It should have some kind of weakness.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.01,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosives.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How much C4 do you have left?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.55,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm down if you have a plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.84,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't care how bad the odds are.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how outlaws are, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.37,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.91,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you could flank us that easily?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way. Move, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.23,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.25,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, eyes forward! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.00,0:14:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Don't let them through!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.34,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do? We can't just destroy the store.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a grenade?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! But watch this!
