Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.72,0:20:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a very difficult situation.\nGood job{! media} getting through it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.83,0:21:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.05,0:21:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls, too.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10}You really saved us there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.29,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You really saved us there.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:04.01,0:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10\fad(0,300)}Thank you, truly.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.01,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, truly.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:05.67,0:21:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10}Th-That was hardly worth thanking us for.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.67,0:21:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was hardly worth thanking us for.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10\fad(0,300)}All in a day's work for first-class outlaws.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All in a day's work for first-class outlaws.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it was, with how fired up you were!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell them that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for the next part.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.57,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're coming for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you attack Abydos?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.35,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you confused about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.23,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be sure to repay over half of the school's debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.66,0:21:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what we agreed on, was it not?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.53,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,now that you have dropped out,\nthe student council no longer has any members.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It could hardly be considered a school at this point.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.93,0:22:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole situation with Abydos\nis a mere preamble to the real event.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.57,0:22:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.94,0:22:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our eyes were set on you from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.26,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed you to sign that contract\nand surrender all your rights to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.66,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And to reach that end, we cooperated\nwith the Kaiser Corporation.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.42,0:22:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They were merely pawns.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.75,0:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise if you misunderstood my position,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.56,0:22:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was never employed at that petty corporation.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.51,0:22:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've attained the strongest Mystic in Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly waste that\non mere mercenary work, now could I?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.47,0:22:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This fascinating experiment\nis what we've yearned to witness.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.38,0:23:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that clears up our intentions.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.45,0:23:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet again,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.93,0:23:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been tricked by an adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.25,0:23:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.46,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.14,0:23:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nonomi{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.82,0:23:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serika{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.11,0:23:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.40,0:23:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.64,0:23:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yume{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.49,0:23:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{=3}{\i1}I'm sorry.

